子住在深圳福田，該警員數日前放假，並曾到內地探望妻子，回港後發燒，昨（22日）入住仁濟醫院隔離病房，正等候快速測試結果。據了解，該交通部警員因應反修例運動，被借調到防暴隊，負責駐守重點建築物，如政總及警總。該警員4、5日前下班後回內地，回港後再未有上班。東九龍行動基地內已加強消毒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警隊內部流傳東九龍機動部隊一名警員妻子曾到武漢，妻子回港後咳嗽，但警員未有發燒，警員及家人現正在醫院接受檢查，觀塘警署已加強消毒。本報正就有關消息向警方查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">THIS?????</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:20:19.000Z","msg":"狗總<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f5af66de61a09e263645baa2107ddd306c0a03","tid":1837303,"uid":239821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbba77ddfcea631370c104c6301970ef038deb4a","tid":1837303,"uid":62935,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"bce76fc539a719079088a5a1f2693f119b4c4a8d","tid":1837303,"uid":73026,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"初部確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:15:13.000Z","msg":"中期確診<br />\n三度確診<br />\n後期確診<br />\n末期確診"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95653e719a9554b4650ae8a99ed1d94a5089011","tid":1837303,"uid":54195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb326d7689981c95378ca7cc0e912e5f7990a175","tid":1837303,"uid":110456,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020