子，回港後發燒，昨（22日）入住仁濟醫院隔離病房，正等候快速測試結果。據了解，該交通部警員因應反修例運動，被借調到防暴隊，負責駐守重點建築物，如政總及警總。該警員4、5日前下班後回內地，回港後再未有上班。東九龍行動基地內已加強消毒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警隊內部流傳東九龍機動部隊一名警員妻子曾到武漢，妻子回港後咳嗽，但警員未有發燒，警員及家人現正在醫院接受檢查，觀塘警署已加強消毒。本報正就有關消息向警方查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">THIS?????</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"上天回應訴求?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fa630c52b747754d04dda89aec9bf3541298ef","tid":1837303,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59bdf2eb9c0bdb037bc1cb48c3b4a6e30e7ff479","tid":1837303,"uid":302890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"初步確診即係係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係度搬弄語言藝術"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:36:54.000Z","msg":"今次又叫初步確診？唔係初步懷疑？<br />\n頭兩單兩次陽性都係叫高度懷疑，唔叫確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bda63359ef8eb5662503476b30fb23a1788026","tid":1837303,"uid":301152,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f01780122e628890fdf6a5a9680ca9d85becee6d","tid":1837303,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bce76fc539a719079088a5a1f2693f119b4c4a8d","tid":1837303,"uid":73026,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T14:41:42.000Z","msg":"初部確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"高度懷疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T15:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死之前確定唔到就唔計 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sc1f7Vp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http